            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 1.6.0</h2>
                <h3>✨ New Features</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Direct touch from your phone or tablet</strong> — When you control your Mac from an iPhone or iPad, your touches now feel like a real touchscreen — tap, scroll, pinch-to-zoom, and drag work naturally without being awkwardly translated into mouse moves and clicks.</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>🐛 Bug Fixes</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Fixed a launch crash</strong> — Resolved a rare startup crash on macOS where the app would quit immediately on first launch. The app now reliably starts on every Mac.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
